trans-unit.source: Represents a common dialog box that allows a user to specify a filename for one or more files to open.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en vanlig dialogboks der en bruker til å angi et filnavn for én eller flere filer til å åpne.

trans-unit.source: The following figure shows an OpenFileDialog for [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_winvista](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-winvista-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: Illustrasjonen nedenfor viser en OpenFileDialog for [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_winvista](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-winvista-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: ![Open dialog box](~/add/media/dialogboxesoverviewfigure2.png "Open dialog box") Starting in [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winvista](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-winvista-md.md)], open and save file dialog boxes have a **Favorite Links** panel on the left side of the dialog box that allows the user to quickly navigate to a different location.
trans-unit.target: ![Åpne dialogboksen](~/add/media/dialogboxesoverviewfigure2.png "åpen dialogboks") starter i [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winvista](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-winvista-md.md)]ved å åpne og lagre dialogbokser har en **koblinger** panelet til venstre i dialogboksen som gir brukeren mulighet til å navigere raskt til en annen plassering.

trans-unit.source: These links are called custom places.
trans-unit.target: Disse koblingene kalles egendefinerte steder.

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:Microsoft.Win32.FileDialog.CustomPlaces%2A> property to set this list of links.
trans-unit.target: Bruk av <xref:Microsoft.Win32.FileDialog.CustomPlaces%2A>til å angi denne listen over koblinger.</xref:Microsoft.Win32.FileDialog.CustomPlaces%2A>

trans-unit.source: ## XAML Text Usage You cannot declare this managed class in [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: ## XAML teksten Bruk du kan ikke deklarere denne administrerte klassen i [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="Microsoft.Win32.OpenFileDialog"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="Microsoft.Win32.OpenFileDialog"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets an option indicating whether <xref href="Microsoft.Win32.OpenFileDialog"></xref> allows users to select multiple files.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir et alternativ som angir om <xref href="Microsoft.Win32.OpenFileDialog"> </xref> kan brukerne velge flere filer.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if multiple selections are allowed; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis flere valg er tillatt. Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standard <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Opens a read-only stream for the file that is selected by the user using <xref href="Microsoft.Win32.OpenFileDialog"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Åpner en skrivebeskyttet dataflyt for filen som er valgt av brukeren ved hjelp av <xref href="Microsoft.Win32.OpenFileDialog"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The file is opened with read-only permission (<xref:System.IO.FileMode>, <xref:System.IO.FileAccess>, and <xref:System.IO.FileShare>), whether or not the Read Only checkbox is checked in the dialog.
trans-unit.target: Filen åpnes med lesetilgang (<xref:System.IO.FileMode>, <xref:System.IO.FileAccess>, og <xref:System.IO.FileShare>), hvorvidt det skrivebeskyttet er merket av i dialogboksen.</xref:System.IO.FileShare> </xref:System.IO.FileAccess> </xref:System.IO.FileMode>

trans-unit.source: Because the file is opened without the ability to overwrite or write to the file, an application can safely load a file while executing within partial trust restrictions.
trans-unit.target: Fordi filen åpnes uten mulighet til å overskrive eller skrive til filen, kan en applikasjon trygt laste inn en fil under utføring i delvis klarering begrensninger.

trans-unit.source: If more than one file is selected, the first selected file is opened.
trans-unit.target: Hvis mer enn én fil er valgt, er den første merkede filen åpnes.

trans-unit.source: A new <xref:System.IO.Stream> that contains the selected file.
trans-unit.target: En ny <xref:System.IO.Stream>som inneholder den valgte filen.</xref:System.IO.Stream>

trans-unit.source: No files were selected in the dialog.
trans-unit.target: Ingen filer ble valgt i dialogboksen.

trans-unit.source: Creates an array that contains one read-only stream for each file selected by the user using <xref href="Microsoft.Win32.OpenFileDialog"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en matrise som inneholder en skrivebeskyttet flyt for hver fil som er valgt av brukeren ved hjelp av <xref href="Microsoft.Win32.OpenFileDialog"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Each file is opened with read-only permission (<xref:System.IO.FileMode>, <xref:System.IO.FileAccess>, and <xref:System.IO.FileShare>), whether or not the Read Only checkbox is checked in the dialog.
trans-unit.target: Hver fil åpnes med lesetilgang (<xref:System.IO.FileMode>, <xref:System.IO.FileAccess>, og <xref:System.IO.FileShare>), hvorvidt det skrivebeskyttet er merket av i dialogboksen.</xref:System.IO.FileShare> </xref:System.IO.FileAccess> </xref:System.IO.FileMode>

trans-unit.source: Because each file is opened without the ability to overwrite or write to the file, an application can safely load one or more files while executing within partial trust restrictions.
trans-unit.target: Fordi hver fil åpnes uten mulighet til å overskrive eller skrive til filen, kan en applikasjon trygt laste inn én eller flere filer under kjøring i delvis klarering begrensninger.

trans-unit.source: An array of multiple new <xref:System.IO.Stream> objects that contain the selected files.
trans-unit.target: En matrise av flere nye <xref:System.IO.Stream>objekter som inneholder de valgte filene.</xref:System.IO.Stream>

trans-unit.source: No files were selected in the dialog.
trans-unit.target: Ingen filer ble valgt i dialogboksen.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value indicating whether the read-only check box displayed by <xref href="Microsoft.Win32.OpenFileDialog"></xref> is selected.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om merket for skrivebeskyttet vises av <xref href="Microsoft.Win32.OpenFileDialog"> </xref> er valgt.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the checkbox is selected; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis det er merket i avmerkingsboksen. Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standard <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Resets all <xref href="Microsoft.Win32.OpenFileDialog"></xref> properties to their default values.
trans-unit.target: Tilbakestiller alle <xref href="Microsoft.Win32.OpenFileDialog"> </xref> egenskapene til standardverdiene.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value indicating whether <xref href="Microsoft.Win32.OpenFileDialog"></xref> contains a read-only check box.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om <xref href="Microsoft.Win32.OpenFileDialog"> </xref> inneholder en avmerkingsboks for skrivebeskyttet.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the checkbox is displayed; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis vises i avmerkingsboksen. Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standard <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.
